# terms ###########################
RABBIT - root user
OTOPSK - One Time Only Pre Shared Key
ANONI - jail world of day traffic
HIVE - DEMON hive workers
SICC - archive System In Complete Chaos
CHRON - network time & system cycles
CLAN - capisum network groups
PF - explicit-network-traffic pipes
CONF - network sha-verified configurations
NOTARY - sha-verified witness
INIT - pipe-highway establish
BANK - $KEY exchange reputation
$SKEY - usb access-keys
PASS - thermal-printed access-keys
# users ###########################
norm - basic jail shells
seer - mods connected to a lord
lord - capisum lords of system
